casebody.data:
No. 11-6521. Assem A. Abulkhair, Petitioner v. Menelaos Toskos, et al. 565 U.S. 1051, 132 S. Ct. 771,

181 L. Ed. 2d 475,

2011 U.S. LEXIS 8361. November 28, 2011.

Motion of petitioner for leave to proceed in forma pau-peris denied, and petition for writ of cer-tiorari to the United States Court of Appeals for the Third Circuit dismissed. See Rule 39.8.

Same case below, 430 Fed. Appx. 98.
